{"tid":237900,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] [廣東先羸1分] 清遠居民罷市罷課 政府跪低放棄建焚化廠","createTime":"2017-05-10T16:37:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-11T19:12:42.000Z","uid":31637,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c106df8a4171994aa839772350ec326cbf49d220","tid":237900,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T16:37:57.000Z","msg":"廣東清遠市數萬居民針對飛來峽鎮政府興建垃圾焚化廠的抗議行動，持續了一星期，昨晚更爆發警民衝突，警方施放催淚彈驅趕抗議者。昨晚起有至少800多名武警到該鎮，並把鎮的出入口全部封鎖，且有人剪網線要封鎖當地網絡。今日，飛來峽鎮居民持續罷市罷課，並一度傳出會斷水斷電。<br />\n<br />\n今日下午，村民張小姐向《蘋果》指，鎮政府領導剛向示威的鄉親宣佈，放棄在當地興建焚化廠的計劃。她指，鄉親經過連日在鎮政府門口「文明抗爭」後，示威將暫時結束，「大家都好累，要返去休息下」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170510/56677399\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170510%2F56677399&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=eddb0477\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170510%2F56677399&h=284a7a58\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170510/56677399</a>"},{"pid":"1f4b753a93b69beadf5ff4d3f7157a759cef0e3d","tid":237900,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T16:39:38.000Z","msg":"搬黎香港起咪搞掂"},{"pid":"6590d1c81f5fcd6faceb92d12b21c1804d3dcd46","tid":237900,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T16:43:17.000Z","msg":"嘩 以後點管治啊 政府好難做嘢㗎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbd6986539bc2f6b51369e5d0622b7a2bc46f15e","tid":237900,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T16:46:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b63ee1c3b14e407cdddfa515d7d410ac22be9bd3","tid":237900,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T16:47:58.000Z","msg":"有線有片睇:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/673701076155297/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F673701076155297%2F&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=d5254f21\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/673701076155297/</a><br />\n<br />\n廣東清遠自周日起，有大批民眾上街示威，抗議政府計劃在距離市中心三十分鐘車程的飛來峽鎮，興建垃圾焚燒發電廠。<br />\n事件後來演變成警民衝突，公安周二晚施放催淚彈驅散示威民眾。<br />\n當地政府及後發表聲明，決定取消興建垃圾焚燒發電廠，指決定是考慮民眾的反對意見後，認為民眾是出於對清遠的關懷同受護，並指中共清遠市委、市政府尊重科學、尊重民意，及重視環保。"},{"pid":"ffff6e4699bc1eccea5e77fdb8a058b16d51d43b","tid":237900,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T16:48:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"103e23c79655b26ecf98aee1da7c0180887d9bad","tid":237900,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T16:50:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有線有片睇:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/673701076155297/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F673701076155297%2F&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=d5254f21\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/673701076155297/</a><br />\n<br />\n廣東清遠自周日起，有大批民眾上街示威，抗議政府計劃在距離市中心三十分鐘車程的飛來峽鎮，興建垃圾焚燒發電廠。<br />\n事件後來演變成警民衝突，公安周二晚施放催淚彈驅散示威民眾。<br />\n當地政府及後發表聲明，決定取消興建垃圾焚燒發電廠，指決定是考慮民眾的反對意見後，認為民眾是出於對清遠的關懷同受護，並指中共清遠市委、市政府尊重科學、尊重民意，及重視環保。</blockquote><br />\n香港應該同清遠接軌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34c6ba0aa298f5075cf75d57751f9d33bca6bcab","tid":237900,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T17:02:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ddac1bc042653a40b098937050b724a4f09d5b8","ti